{"tid":1563480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動] 可唔可以開番個＂行動＂分台！！！","createTime":"2019-09-12T12:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T01:09:35.000Z","uid":182291,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e50d6194b7fb38908d2730cf30286f68a191d878","tid":1563480,"uid":182291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:00:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">依家咩消防男神國歌 post 上曬熱門， 唔係話唔好， 但係啲行動 post 俾其他 post 推走曬。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地可唔可以整番個＂行動＂分台大家一㩒就睇到曬有咩行動。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n唔好話驚 mon post 狗，人地mon post 狗24小時mon post 要搵到行動post一定搵到，<span style=\"color: red;\">有分台反而係方便自己人睇有咩行動，俾人推走都唔怕。</span>唔係個個人都成日on 到line, 可能一日上成呢幾次。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><br />\n我要【行動】分台！！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b743fb743f43c080d610318a361ebfe130c885c5","tid":1563480,"uid":182291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:00:29.000Z","msg":"Push 1/10"},{"pid":"25991a149c62606ddb2b10e1210fa3498a6bdbb5","tid":1563480,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:00:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"a3ce2bb7b74bb57f5266d4d06c7ce4bb244b8963","tid":1563480,"uid":249390